            <h2>Fun Facts About Lambs</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Lambs are known for their playful nature and can often be seen jumping and running around, which is called 'gamboling'.</li>
                <li>A baby sheep is called a lamb, and they can recognize their mother's voice soon after birth.</li>
                <li>Lambs have a strong social bond and often form friendships with other lambs.</li>
                <li>Their woolly coats not only keep them warm but also make them excellent swimmers!</li>
